<i> Tidak, Han Do Joon.
Kau tidak bisa berhenti di sini. </i>

45
00:03:33,820 --> 00:03:39,010
<i> Yeo Jin, polisi?
Mereka akan berlutut dihadapanku. </i>

46
00:03:39,010 --> 00:03:40,970
Tentu, Komisaris.

47
00:03:40,970 --> 00:03:43,840
Tolong, jaga dia.

48
00:03:43,840 --> 00:03:45,460
Karena dia sakit.

49
