00:10:01,880 --> 00:10:05,400
Sekarang, ayo pergi.

125
00:10:07,020 --> 00:10:09,570
Ayo.

126
00:10:40,060 --> 00:10:42,190
Iya. Ya, aku mengerti!

127
00:10:43,600 --> 00:10:45,560
Tim Keamanan Dua, ikuti aku!

128
00:11:14,420 --> 00:11:16,590
Selamat datang kembali,
Nona Young Ae!

129
00:11:16,590 --> 00:11:20,370
- Maksudku, Presdir.
- Selamat, Presdir.

130
00:11:23,650 --> 00:11:25,590
- Periksa keluar.
- Ya!

131
00:11:29,880 --> 00:11:31,950
- Beri jalan.
- Ya, Presdir.

132
00:11:31,950 --> 00:11:33,480
Semuanya, minggir!

133
00:12:37,730 --> 00:12:41,500
Alasan aku bisa
kembali dengan selamat hari ini...

134
00:12:41,500 --> 00:12:44,270
